{"tid":390820,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真問]有冇巴絲拍開片?？","createTime":"2017-09-07T10:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T04:42:58.000Z","uid":62225,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8115b7559424640cb8f4591c19cc3c7c7ad5912a","tid":390820,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:32:39.000Z","msg":"[戴頭盔mode]，今次係真宣傳！<br />\n <br />\n搞緊個短片創作比賽，希望用短片形式收集青少年嘅心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暑假個陣，開左一堆post知道其實好多巴絲對拍片剪片有興趣，所以都係到借個位宣傳下。推介呢個比賽俾有心嘅巴絲參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實好簡單，2-6 mins 既片，類型不限。想透過大家鍾意短片呢個興趣去帶起呢一個主題比唔同既人去睇。<br />\n你話我呃人又好，追數又好，咩都好。真心勿小，有好東西同大家介紹下only。<br />\n<br />\n下面有活動詳情: <br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/OeZUfbGsnmQ0xsMu2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FOeZUfbGsnmQ0xsMu2&d=Q3kjnObNMURrvSdCA%2Bi%2BKm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7976ab2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/OeZUfbGsnmQ0xsMu2</a><br />\n<br />\nbtw，大家有咩ideas或者困難都可以係呢個post集思廣益一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7920996131abf7517aa8c2060029da703f42fc22","tid":390820,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:45:11.000Z","msg":"個post咁多負皮仲話好多巴絲想拍片？"},{"pid":"e6e54167025b1e048259499afc3d6baec35dd9b4","tid":390820,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:27:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個post咁多負皮仲話好多巴絲想拍片？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯 好多負評 但好多人報左名<br />\n唔明點解。"},{"pid":"9a2d654752c8f2765f775d9b5909c3295309f3cf","tid":390820,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T16:16